Yawan kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) a cikin Tarayyar Turai ko Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya, daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020
Yawan kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) ya nuna irin wannan yanayin a kasashen Tarayyar Turai ko Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya, wanda ya tabbatar da cewa, ko da yake a matakai daban-daban dangane da ƙasar, cutar COVID-19 tana ci gaba da sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Bisa ga kwarewar Italiya, ƙasashe, asibitoci da wuraren kulawa mai tsanani suna buƙatar haɓaka shirye-shiryen su don raƙuman marasa lafiya na COVID-19 waɗanda zasu buƙaci kulawar likita, musamman kulawar gaggawa.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, an samu rahoton wasu cututtukan cutar huhu da ba a san su ba a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 9 ga watan Janairun 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cututtuka ta kasar Sin ta ruwaito cewa mai haddasa cutar coronavirus ne wanda yanzu ake kira coronavirus 2 na cutar ta numfashi mai tsanani (SARS-CoV-2).
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 ta haifar an kira ta cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
Bayanai sun nuna cewa kashi 80 cikin dari na mutanen da ke fama da cutar COVID-19 suna da wata cuta mai sauƙi, wato kamuwa da cutar numfashi tare da ko ba tare da cutar huhu ba, kuma yawancin suna warkewa.
A cikin kashi 14 cikin dari na shari'o'in, COVID-19 ya ci gaba zuwa wani mummunan cuta wanda ke buƙatar asibiti, yayin da sauran kashi 6 cikin dari na shari'o'in ke haɓaka mummunan cuta wanda ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani.
Mutuwar marasa lafiya da ke asibiti saboda COVID-19 ya kai kashi 4 cikin 100.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun bincika yanayin da ake samu na COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta Tarayyar Turai ko Ƙasar Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EU/EEA) da Burtaniya (UK) kuma mun kwatanta su da na lardin Hubei, China.
Mun kuma kwatanta adadin shari'o'in COVID-19 na yanzu a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya da na Italiya daga Janairu 31 zuwa Maris 15, 2020.
Kasashen EU/EEA da Birtaniya sun kamu da cutar COVID-19
Bayan China, COVID-19 ya ci gaba da yaduwa a fannin duniya kuma motsin cutar COVID-19 a sauran duniya a halin yanzu yana ci gaba da wannan ƙasar.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, babban darektan Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A cikin fitowar 5 ga Maris na Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri et al. sun ba da rahoton farkon tabbatar da shari'o'in COVID-19 a Turai bisa ga ma'anar shari'ar WHO.
A cikin EU/EEA, an fara samun mutane uku da aka tabbatar da cutar a Faransa a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020, a cikin mutanen da suka dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an gano shari'o'in COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen 30 na EU / EEA da Burtaniya (RU), bisa ga abin da tsakanin 31 ga Disamba na 2019 zuwa wannan ranar har ma, an yi rikodin shari'o'i 39 768 da mutuwar 1727, daga cikinsu 17 750 da mutuwar 1441 sun faru a Italiya kawai.
Samun adadin da aka samu da kuma yawan kamuwa da cutar COVID-19
A Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC), ana sabunta ƙididdigar shari'o'in COVID-19 da aka ruwaito a kowace ƙasa a duniya, wanda aka samo daga tushen hukuma kawai, kamar Ma'aikatar Lafiya ta ƙasashe, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki da WHO, kowace rana a karfe 8:00 na safe.
An yi amfani da wannan bayanan ne don bincika yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya da kuma kwatanta su da na Italiya.
A matsayin mai nuna alamun yawan mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar COVID-19, mun ƙididdige yawan adadin COVID-19 da aka yanke zuwa kwanaki 14; ta wannan hanyar, mun yi la'akari da yanayin COVID-19, a kowace ƙasa ta EU / EEA da Burtaniya, a lokacin Janairu 1 zuwa Maris 15, 2020.
Mun kuma gabatar da adadin adadin shari'o'in da aka ruwaito a kowace ƙasa zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020, da karfe 8:00 na safe, idan aka kwatanta da na Italiya don lokacin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Yanayin COVID-19 a ƙasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya
Yanayin da aka samu na kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14 a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da Birtaniya gaba ɗaya, ya biyo bayan na lardin Hubei (China) (hoto na 1).
A cikin EU/EEA da UK gabaɗaya, cutar COVID-19 ta fara ƙaruwa a kusa da 21 ga Fabrairu sannan ta ƙaru sosai a kusa da 28 ga Fabrairu 2020 (ƙarin bayani).
Wannan ya kasance ne saboda saurin karuwar adadin shari'o'in da aka ruwaito daga Italiya, amma duk sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya sun nuna abubuwan da suka faru na COVID-19 da suka faru (abubuwan da suka dace).
Hoton 2 ya nuna adadin adadin COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya, idan aka kwatanta da na Italiya a tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Ya ce, a ranar 15 ga Maris da karfe 8:00 na safe, wasu ƙasashen EU/EEA da Birtaniya sun riga sun yi rikodin adadin adadin da ya yi daidai da na Italiya makonni 3 ko ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa adadin shari'o'in COVID-19 da aka ruwaito suna ƙaruwa cikin sauri a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya.
Hanyoyin da aka lura a cikin yawan cutar COVID-19 sun nuna cewa annobar tana ci gaba da irin wannan saurin a duk ƙasashe.
Wannan haka yake duk da matakai daban-daban da kasashe ke ciki, bambance-bambance a cikin amsoshin lafiyar jama'a na ƙasa da, mai yiwuwa, ma'anar shari'a daban-daban a cikin ƙasashe da ladabi daban-daban don zaɓar marasa lafiya waɗanda dole ne su shiga gwajin don tabbatar da COVID-19, gami da jinkirin gwaji.
A farkon watan Maris na shekarar 2020, likitoci a yankunan da cutar ta shafa a Italiya sun bayyana halin da ake ciki inda kashi 10 cikin dari na marasa lafiya da ke fama da COVID-19 ke bukatar kulawa mai tsanani, kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun ruwaito cewa asibitoci da wuraren kula da gaggawa a waɗannan yankuna sun riga sun kai iyakar ƙarfin su.
Bayanai game da shigar da COVID-19 a asibiti ko cibiyar kulawa mai tsanani a halin yanzu suna samuwa a EU/EEA don kashi 6 cikin 100 da 1 cikin 100 na shari'o'in, bi da bi (ba a nuna bayanan ba).
Duk da haka, ya kamata a tattara su a cikin tsari don ƙarin bayanan kulawa na yanzu wanda ke mai da hankali kan yawan shari'o'in da aka bayar da rahoto da yawan mutuwar.
Wani bincike da aka yi a shekara ta 201011 ya nuna cewa akwai babban canji a yawan gado na kulawa mai tsanani da kuma na matsakaici a Turai, daga 29.2 a Jamus zuwa 4.2 a cikin mazauna 100 000 a Portugal.
Wannan yana nufin cewa ƙasashe za su iya samun albarkatu fiye da Italiya (wurin yin barci na gaggawa da kuma na matsakaici a kowace mutane 100,000 a 201011).
An ba da misali na yanayin cikawar iyawar kula da lafiya, tare da ƙididdiga ga kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da Burtaniya na yawan cututtukan asibiti na COVID-19 da ke da alaƙa da haɗarin >90% na ƙaruwa a cikin ƙarfin gado na kulawa mai tsanani, a cikin sabuntawa ta shida na ECDC na COVID-19 saurin kimantawa.
