Kwarewar Italiya da abubuwan da ke faruwa a yanzu a wasu ƙasashe sun nuna cewa annobar COVID-19 tana ci gaba da sauri a cikin EU / EEA da Burtaniya.
Saboda haka, dole ne kasashe, asibitoci da wuraren kula da gaggawa su shirya don yanayin watsawar SARS-CoV-2 na al'umma da kuma karuwar yawan marasa lafiya da ke fama da COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kulawar likita, musamman, kulawar gaggawa, kamar yadda ke faruwa a yankunan da aka shafa a Italiya.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin saurin kimanta haɗarin ECDC, yana da mahimmanci a ɗauki hanzari, mai aiki, da kuma cikakkiyar hanyar da za a jinkirta yaduwar SARS-CoV-2, tare da sauyawa daga hanyar dakile zuwa hanyar ragewa, saboda ƙimar da aka yi hasashen yawan lokuta na iya ba da isasshen lokaci ga masu yanke shawara da asibitoci don fahimta, yarda da daidaita amsar su yadda ya kamata idan ba a aiwatar da su ba da wuri.
Har ila yau, saurin tantance haɗari ya lissafa matakan kiwon lafiyar jama'a da ake buƙata don rage tasirin cutar.
Akwai ɗan gajeren lokaci na dama a lokacin da ƙasashe ke da damar zurfafa ƙoƙarin sarrafa su don hana yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da rage matsin lamba akan tsarin kiwon lafiya.
Idan ba a yi haka ba, tsarin kiwon lafiya na sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA na iya fuskantar raƙuman marasa lafiya da ke bukatar kulawa mai tsanani a cikin kwanaki da makonni masu zuwa.
Cutar cutar coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), wadda ta haifar da cutar coronavirus 2 ta rikicin numfashi mai tsanani (SARS) (SARS-CoV-2), har zuwa yanzu ta kashe mutane 3000 kuma ta kamu da fiye da mutane 80,000 a China da sauran wurare a duniya, wanda ya haifar da bala'i ga mutane.
Kamar yadda yake da cutar SARS-CoV, wadda ta haifar da SARS a dubban mutane a 2003, SARS-CoV-2 ma zai iya kamuwa daga bats kuma ya haifar da irin wannan bayyanar ta hanyar irin wannan tsari.
Koyaya, COVID-19 yana da ƙarancin tsanani da mutuwa fiye da SARS, amma yana da yawa fiye da watsawa kuma yana shafar tsofaffi fiye da matasa kuma yana shafar maza fiye da mata.
A sakamakon yawan wallafe-wallafen da ake yi game da cutar da ke tasowa, manufar wannan labarin ita ce samar da cikakken bincike na bincike a kan batun, wanda ke faruwa da sauri.
Za mu tattauna muhimman fannoni na cututtuka, etiology, virology, ganewar asali, magani, tsinkaya da rigakafin cutar.
Ko da yake ba a amsa tambayoyi da yawa ba, muna fata wannan bincike zai taimaka mana mu fahimci wannan cuta mai tsanani kuma mu kawar da ita.
Bikin bazara na 25 ga Janairu na 2020 ya zama abin tunawa da ba a taɓa ji ba ga duk Sinawa, waɗanda aka ƙarfafa su su zauna a gida a duk lokacin bikin kuma har tsawon makonni da yawa saboda barkewar sabuwar cuta ta kwayar cuta.
Wannan kwayar cutar tana da kusan iri ɗaya da cutar coronavirus (CoV) wanda ya haifar da barkewar cutar ta cutar ta numfashi mai tsanani (SARS) a shekara ta 2003; saboda haka, a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta kira ta SARS-CoV-2, kuma cutar da ke tattare da ita ta kira cutar coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Cutar ta fara ne a birnin Wuhan na kasar Sin kuma ta bazu cikin sauri a fadin kasar da kuma kusan kasashe 50 a duniya.
A ranar 2 ga Maris, 2020, cutar ta haifar da fiye da 80 000 da aka tabbatar da COVID-19, tare da fiye da 40 000 marasa lafiya da aka sake su kuma fiye da 3000 marasa lafiya sun mutu.
Hukumar ta WHO ta yi gargadin cewa COVID-19 ita ce babbar magabcin jama'a kuma tana da iko fiye da ta'addanci.
A cewar PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), a cikin kasa da watanni biyu, an wallafa labarai na kimiyya sama da 200 game da COVID-19, gami da virology, epidemiology, etiology, diagnosis da magani, tun daga rahoton farko na Janairu 7, 2020, wanda ya ƙayyade jerin cututtukan da aka keɓe daga marasa lafiya da yawa.
Manufar wannan bincike ita ce taƙaita ci gaban bincike a kan wannan sabon batun da ke ci gaba da sauri.
A duk lokacin da zai yiwu, za mu gwada COVID-19 da SARS da kuma wani cuta da COVID ke haifarwa, ciwon numfashi na Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS, barkewar cutar a shekarar 2012).
Za mu kuma bincika abin da aka sani game da rigakafi da kuma tsinkayar cutar, da kuma wasu tambayoyi masu muhimmanci da ba a amsa su ba tukuna.
Ana ganin cewa cutar coronavirus ba ta mutuwa ba ce ga mutane, kuma a yawancin lokuta tana haifar da kusan kashi 15 cikin 100 na mura 4.
Duk da haka, a wannan karni, mun sami cututtukan coronavirus sau biyu masu cutarwa a cikin mutane, wato SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, wanda suka haifar da barkewar cutar a China, a 2003, da Saudi Arabia, a 2012, bi da bi, kuma nan da nan suka bazu zuwa wasu ƙasashe da yawa tare da mummunan kamuwa da cutar da mutuwar.
Saboda haka, barkewar cutar COVID-19 ta yanzu ita ce ta uku ta coronavirus da aka yi rikodin a tarihin bil'adama.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a Fig. 1,1, an fara bayar da rahoton tarin cututtukan huhu na asali da ba a sani ba a ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019 daga Wuhan zuwa Hukumar Lafiya ta kasar Sin.
Bayan kwana bakwai, an sanar da jerin sunayen cutar coronavirus.
A ranar 15 ga Janairu, 2020, an yi rikodin mutuwar farko a Wuhan.
A halin yanzu, annobar ta bazu cikin sauri zuwa birane, larduna da ƙasashe makwabta.
A ranar 20 ga watan Janairu, an samu rahoton kamuwa da cutar daga masu ba da kulawar lafiya, wanda ya nuna cewa ana iya watsa ta tsakanin mutane.
A ranar 23 ga watan Janairu, an sanya birnin Wuhan a cikin killace kuma an dakatar da duk jigilar jama'a.
A ranar 24 ga watan Janairu, binciken farko na asibiti kan cutar ya ba da rahoton cewa, daga cikin marasa lafiya 41 da aka tabbatar da cutar, 21 ne kawai suka yi hulɗa kai tsaye da kasuwar kifin teku ta Wuhan wanda aka ɗauka wuri ne na asalin kamuwa da cutar daga asalin dabba da ba a sani ba.
A ranar 30 ga Janairu, WHO ta ayyana barkewar cutar a matsayin gaggawa na kiwon lafiya a duniya.
A lokacin da aka ba da rahoton, cutar ta riga ta bazu ko'ina cikin Sin da kuma kusan ƙasashe 50 a duniya (Fig. 2).
Tun da yanayin ya ci gaba da sauri, ba a iya ƙayyade girman da kuma tsanani na ƙarshe na barkewar cutar ba tukuna.
A ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, wani bincike mai yawa na marasa lafiya 8866, ciki har da marasa lafiya 4021 da aka tabbatar da COVID-19, ya gabatar da ƙarin bayani na cutar da aka bayyana a ƙasa (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
