An saki kwayoyin RNA na kwayar cuta zuwa cikin cytoplasm; bayan an sake kwayar kwayoyin cuta, RNA na kwayar cuta, tare da glycoproteins na ɓoye da furotin nucleocapside, suna haifar da ƙwayoyin cuta waɗanda ke dauke da virions, waɗanda daga baya suka haɗu da membrane na plasma don sakin kwayar cuta.
