Waɗannan matakan suna da tasiri wajen rage haɗarin kamuwa da cuta da kuma hana yaduwar cutar.
Ko da yake SARS-CoV-2 ya bayyana a matsayin sabon kwayar cutar ga duniyar ɗan adam, babban kamanceceniya da SARS-CoV, kamar yadda aka ruwaito a ranar 7 ga Janairu, 2020, ya kamata ya haifar da babban faɗakarwa a China saboda kwarewar da ta samu daga barkewar SARS a 2003.
Sai dai a ranar 19 ga watan Janairun 2020 ne shugaban Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Wuhan ya kwantar da hankalin 'yan kasar inda ya ce sabon kwayar cutar tana da karancin kamuwa da cutar da kuma iyakance karfin haihuwa tsakanin mutane, kuma babu wata matsala wajen hana da kuma dakile cutar.
Wannan sakon ya rage tsananin fargaba a cikin jama'a, musamman a lokacin da duk kasar ke shirin bikin bazara, kuma an yi amfani da wannan lokacin don rage cutar a ƙarancin sikelin a Wuhan.
Hukumar kula da cututtuka ta kasar Sin ta kamata ta koyi darasi daga wannan mummunan abu kuma ta yi gagarumin gyara a nan gaba.
Alal misali, waɗannan hukumomi ya kamata su kasance (1) masu hankali wajen yin sanarwa ga jama'a, tun da kowane kalma tana da mahimmanci ga 'yan ƙasa kuma tana iya sa su canza hali ko yanke shawara; (2) masu saurin fahimta da kuma amsawa ga bayanan da ba a saba gani ba daga asibitoci, maimakon jiran rahotanni na yau da kullun daga likitoci ko jami'ai; (3) masu ƙuntatawa don hana yiwuwar annobar a farkon matakin, maimakon ƙoƙarin tabbatar da jama'a; da (4) masu daidaitawa a cikin aiwatar da daidaitaccen da ingantattun horo don haɓaka wayar da kan jama'a game da cututtukan annobar da kuma gwadawa da inganta tsarin amsawar jama'a a kai a kai.
Cutar COVID-19 da sabon kwayar cutar SARS-CoV-2 ta haifar ta fara ne a ƙarshen Disamba na 2019.
A cikin kasa da watanni biyu, ya bazu ko'ina cikin kasar Sin da kuma wasu kasashe 50 a duniya a lokacin da aka yi wannan bincike.
Tun da cutar ta yi kama da SARS-CoV kuma akwai kamanceceniya tsakanin alamun COVID-19 da SARS, barkewar COVID-19 ta haifar da jin kamar SARS ta sake bayyana.
Duk da haka, akwai wasu bambance-bambance masu ban mamaki tsakanin COVID-19 da SARS, waɗanda ke da mahimmanci don dakile cutar da kuma kula da marasa lafiya.
COVID-19 ya fi rinjayar tsofaffi fiye da matasa da maza fiye da mata, kuma tsanani da mutuwa sun fi girma a cikin tsofaffi fiye da matasa.
SARS na da yawan mutuwa fiye da COVID-19 (10,91%) idan aka kwatanta da 1.44%.
Marasa lafiya da COVID-19 suna watsa kwayar cutar ko da ba su da wata alama, yayin da marasa lafiya da SARS yawanci suna yin hakan lokacin da suke da mummunan rashin lafiya, wanda ke haifar da matsala mafi girma wajen dakile yaduwar COVID-19 idan aka kwatanta da SARS.
Wannan ya bayyana, a wani ɓangare, dalilin da ya sa SARS-CoV-2 ya bazu cikin sauri da kuma yaduwa fiye da SARS-CoV.
Gwajin RNA na yau da kullun don SARS-CoV-2 na iya zama mara kyau ga wasu marasa lafiya da COVID-19.
A wani bangare kuma, marasa lafiya da suka warke za su iya sake samun cutar.
Waɗannan sakamakon sun ƙara haɗarin yaduwar cutar sosai.
Ganin ci gaban da ake samu cikin bincike kan COVID-19, akwai wasu muhimman batutuwa da ba a warware ba, kamar su:
Daga ina SARS-CoV-2 ya fito?
Ko da yake an gano kashi 96 cikin dari na homology tsakanin SARS-CoV-2 da kuma coronavirus guda biyu na bats masu kama da SARS, har yanzu ba a iya kammala cewa SARS-CoV-2 ya fito ne daga bats.
Wane dabba ne ya ba da cutar daga mahaifar farko, wato, ƙuƙwalwa, zuwa ga mutane?
Idan ba a san amsoshin da aka ba da a lambobin 1 da 2, ba za a iya hana watsawar ba yadda ya kamata, kuma cutar za ta iya sake barkewa a kowane lokaci.
Ko da yake samfurin kwayoyin halitta da gwaje-gwajen sinadarai sun nuna cewa SARS-CoV-2 yana haɗuwa da ACE2, ta yaya ainihin cutar ta shiga cikin ƙwayoyin numfashi kuma ta haifar da canje-canje na cutar?
Shin kwayar cutar tana haɗuwa da ƙwayoyin da ke bayyana ACE2 a wasu gabobin jiki?
Idan babu amsoshi masu kyau ga waɗannan tambayoyin, ba za a iya yin bincike da sauri da kuma magani mai kyau ba.
Har yaushe cutar za ta ci gaba?
Ta yaya kwayar cutar ta samo asali yayin da take watsawa tsakanin mutane?
Shin zai zama annoba ta duniya, zai mutu kamar SARS ko kuma zai sake tashi a kai a kai kamar mura?
Ko da yake zai ɗauki lokaci, yana da muhimmanci mu nemi amsoshin waɗannan tambayoyin da kuma wasu da yawa.
Duk da haka, ko yaya, ba mu da wani zaɓi sai dai mu dakatar da annobar da wuri-wuri kuma mu koma rayuwarmu ta yau da kullun.
Asalin cutar coronavirus a cikin mutane
Cutar da kuma daidaitawa sun sa kwayar cutar ta coronavirus da kuma wadanda suka kai ta, ciki har da mutane, su ci gaba da juyin halitta na tsawon shekaru.
Har zuwa 2003, an san cewa mutum biyu masu cutar coronavirus suna haifar da ƙananan cututtuka, kamar sanyi.
Cutar cutar ta hanyar numfashi mai tsanani (SARS) da kuma cutar numfashi ta Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS) sun juya kudin ta hanyar bayyana yadda cutar coronavirus na iya zama mummunar cuta ga mutane.
Fitowar SARS-CoV-2 a tsakiyar China a ƙarshen 2019 ya sake sanya coronavirus a cikin hankali kuma ya ba mu mamaki tare da babban watsawa da rage ƙwayoyin cuta idan aka kwatanta da ɗan'uwansa, SARS-CoV.
Cutar kwayar cutar coronavirus a cikin mutane zoonosis ce kuma zai taimaka mana mu san asalin cutar coronavirus a cikin mutane.
Yawancin cututtukan coronavirus na mutane sun samo asali ne daga bats, wanda ba su da cutar.
An kuma san baƙi na matsakaiciyar ajiya na wasu coronavirus na mutane.
Gano dabbobi masu baƙi yana da tasiri kai tsaye a rigakafin cututtuka a cikin mutane.
Binciken hulda tsakanin coronavirus da baƙi a cikin dabbobi na iya, ƙari, fitar da mahimman bayanai game da cutar coronavirus a cikin mutane.
A cikin wannan bincike, mun gabatar da cikakken bayanin ilimin da ke akwai game da cututtukan coronavirus bakwai na mutane, tare da jaddada tarihin gano su, da kuma asalin su na zoonotoci da kuma watsa tsakanin jinsuna.
Abin lura, mun kwatanta da kuma kwatanta coronavirus daban-daban na mutane daga hangen nesa na juyin halitta na kwayar cutar da kuma sake haɗuwa da kwayoyin halitta.
Ana nazarin annobar cutar coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) a wannan mahallin.
Bugu da ƙari, an kuma nuna bukatun don canje-canjen baƙi masu nasara da kuma tasirin ci gaban kwayar cutar a cikin tsanani na cutar.
Kwayoyin cutar korona suna cikin dangin Coronaviridae, wanda ya ƙunshi rukuni na kwayoyin RNA mai kyau tare da murfin.
Wadannan kwayoyin, wadanda suke da babban kwayoyin halitta, daga kilobase 26 zuwa 32, a cikin kwayoyin RNA, an kira su coronavirus saboda yanayin su, saboda siffar kambi da suke da shi a karkashin microscope na lantarki.
A bangaren tsarinsa, cutar coronavirus tana da kwayoyin halitta da ba a rarraba su ba, wadanda suke da irin wannan tsari.
Kimanin kashi biyu bisa uku na genom din suna dauke da manyan manyan tsarin karatu guda biyu (ORF1a da ORF1b), wanda ke fassara zuwa polyprotein replicase pp1a da pp1ab.
Ana kuma sarrafa polyproteins har zuwa samar da sunadarai 16 da ba na tsarin ba, da ake kira nsp1~16.
Ragowar ƙwayar halitta tana ɗauke da ORF don furotin na tsarin, ciki har da furotin (S), furotin (E), membrane (M) da nucleoprotein (N).
Hakanan ana sanya wasu nau'ikan sunadarai na musamman na kowane zuriya ta hanyar zuriyar coronavirus daban-daban.
Dangane da bambancin a cikin jerin sunadarai, ana rarraba coronavirus zuwa nau'i hudu (alfacoronavirus, betacoronavirus, gammacoronavirus da deltacoronavirus), daga cikinsu nau'in betacoronavirus ya ƙunshi yawancin kwayar cutar ta ɗan adam kuma an raba shi zuwa layin (A, B, C da D).
Shaidar ilimin halittu ta nuna cewa bats da rodents sune tushen kwayoyin halitta na yawancin alphacoronavirus da betacoronavirus, yayin da tsuntsaye sune babban tanadi na gammacoronavirus da deltacoronavirus.
A cikin dubban shekaru, coronavirus sun ci gaba da ƙetare shingen jinsuna kuma wasu sun fito ne a matsayin manyan cututtukan mutum.
A halin yanzu, an san mutane bakwai da suka kamu da cutar coronavirus.
Daga cikin su, HCoV-229E da HCoV-NL63 alphacoronavirus ne.
Sauran betacoronavirus guda biyar sune HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, coronavirus na rikitarwa mai tsanani na numfashi (SARS-CoV), coronavirus na rikitarwa na numfashi na Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS-CoV), da SARS-CoV-2.
HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 da HCoV-NL63 yawanci suna haifar da bayyanar cututtuka masu sauƙi, kamar sanyi na yau da kullun ko diarrhea.
A gefe guda, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV da kuma sabon gano SARS-CoV-2 suna da cututtuka masu cutarwa kuma suna haifar da kamuwa da cututtukan iska na ƙasa a cikin yawan marasa lafiya, tare da yiwuwar haɓaka cutar ta hankula ta hankula (SDRA) da bayyanar cututtukan huhu.
HCoV-229E na farko, B814, ya ware daga ɓoyewar hanci na marasa lafiya masu sanyi a tsakiyar shekarun 1960.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, an sami ƙarin ilimi ta hanyar cikakken bincike game da HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43, waɗanda ke haifar da alamun da ba su da iyaka.
A gaskiya ma, har zuwa barkewar cutar SARS, an yarda da shi sosai cewa kamuwa da cutar coronavirus a cikin mutane ba ta da lahani.
Cutar SARS da ta barke a shekara ta 2003 ita ce mafi munin a tarihin zamani kuma ta yi wa mutane sama da 8000 kamuwa da cutar, tare da yawan mutuwar kusan kashi 10.
Shekaru goma bayan haka, cutar ta MERS ta kai ga barkewar cutar a yankin Larabawa da ta bazu zuwa sauran duniya.
Sabon cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (2019-nCoV), wanda daga baya aka kira SARS-CoV-2, shine mai haifar da cutar ta cutar coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), wanda ya kashe fiye da rayuka 3120 kuma ya kamu da mutane sama da 91,000 a ranar 3 ga Maris, 2020.
An yi ta yin gargadi kuma dole ne duniya ta shirya don annobar SARS-CoV-2 da ke gabatowa.
Kwayar cutar coronavirus guda bakwai na mutum tana da asalin zoonotic a cikin bats, beraye ko dabbobi na gida.
Akwai shaidu da yawa da suka nuna cewa an samo dukkanin cututtukan coronavirus daga mutane a cikin bats, inda ƙwayoyin cuta suka dace sosai kuma ba su da cutar, amma suna da bambancin kwayoyin halitta.
Cutar COVID-19 ta kawo manyan kalubalen kiwon lafiya, kimiyya, zamantakewa da kuma halin kirki a kasar Sin da sauran duniya.
Bin diddigin asalin cutar coronavirus a cikin mutane yana ba da tsarin fahimtar tarihin halitta, ƙarfin motsawa da abubuwan hana tsalle tsakanin jinsuna.
Wannan kuma na iya jagorantar ko sauƙaƙe gano tanadi da baƙi na dabbobi masu matsakaici da masu haɓaka SARS-CoV-2, wanda zai sami mahimman abubuwan da za su shafi hana yaduwar nan gaba.
A cikin wannan bincike, mun gabatar da cikakken bayanin asalin zoonotic, watsa tsakanin jinsuna da cutar coronavirus ta mutum.
Musamman, mun nuna kuma mun bincika batun gama gari cewa ƙwayoyin cuta na coronavirus na ɗan adam ba su da ƙwayoyin cuta a cikin baƙi na ajiyarsu na halitta, amma sun zama ƙwayoyin cuta bayan watsawa tsakanin nau'ikan zuwa sabon baƙo.
Mun kuma bincika yanayin juyin halitta na kwayar cutar coronavirus a cikin mutane, inda ƙaruwar watsawa yawanci ke haifar da raguwar kamuwa da cuta.
Ana kuma nazarin ci gaban barkewar cutar SARS-CoV-2 a wannan mahallin.
An san game da cutar coronavirus daga dabbobi tun daga ƙarshen shekarun 1930.
Kafin a fara ware nau'in B814 na HCoV-229E daga nasal secretion marasa lafiya da suka kamu da sanyi na yau da kullun, an ware coronavirus daban-daban a cikin dabbobi daban-daban da suka kamu, kamar kaza, linzamin kwamfuta, saniya, alade, cat da kare.
A cikin shekaru da dama da suka gabata, an gano mutum bakwai da ke dauke da cutar coronavirus.
A takaice taƙaitaccen tarihin binciken kwayar cutar ta mutum a cikin tsari na lokaci (tebur na 1) zai zama mai ba da bayani da kuma bayani.
HCoV-229E na farko ya ware daga hanyoyin numfashi na marasa lafiya da ke da kamuwa da cutar ta hanyar numfashi a shekara ta 1966 kuma daga baya, an daidaita shi don girma a cikin layin WI-38 na huhu.
Marasa lafiya da ke dauke da cutar HCoV-229E sun nuna alamun sanyi na kowa, kamar ciwon kai, taurin kai, rashin jin daɗi da kuma ciwon wuya, tare da zazzabi da tari a cikin kashi 10 zuwa 20 cikin dari na lokuta.
Daga baya, a shekara ta 1967, HCoV-OC43 ya ware daga girma na kwayoyin halitta kuma ya wuce a hankali a kwakwalwar berayen da ke shan nono.
Halin cututtukan cututtukan HCoV-OC43 ya yi kama da na HCoV-229E, wanda alamun su na kama da na sauran cututtukan numfashi, kamar cutar mura A da rinoviruses.
HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43 suna rarraba a duniya kuma suna yaduwa a lokacin hunturu, a cikin yanayi mai laushi.
A gaba ɗaya, lokacin yin amfani da waɗannan ƙwayoyin cuta biyu bai kai mako ɗaya ba, sannan kuma lokacin rashin lafiya na kusan makonni biyu.
A cewar wani bincike da aka yi da masu aikin sa kai na mutum, mutanen da ke da lafiya da suka kamu da cutar HCoV-229E sun kamu da sanyi mai tsanani.
Wasu marasa lafiya da ke fama da cutar sun sami kamuwa da cutar ta kasa.
SARS, wanda aka fi sani da atypical pneumonia, ya haifar da annobar farko da cutar coronavirus ta mutum ta haifar a tarihin ɗan adam, kuma wakili na etiological shine SARS-CoV, coronavirus na uku na mutum da aka gano.
An fara samun cutar SARS a ƙarshen shekara ta 2002 a lardin Guangdong, China.
Cutar SARS ta haifar da shari'o'i 8096 da aka ruwaito tare da mutuwar 774 kuma ta bazu a ƙasashe da nahiyoyi da yawa.
Baya ga masu yadawa, an kiyasta cewa kowane hali zai iya haifar da wasu lokuta biyu na biyu, tare da lokacin yin amfani da kwanaki 4 zuwa 7 da kuma farawar mafi girman nauyin kwayar cutar a rana ta goma ta rashin lafiya.
Marasa lafiya da ke dauke da cutar SARS-CoV suna fara da ciwon hanci, ciwon kai, zazzabi, rashin jin daɗi da sanyi, sannan suna da rashin jin daɗi, tari da kuma wahalar numfashi a matsayin alamun rashin lafiya.
Lymphopenia, rashin aikin hanta, da kuma yawan creatine kinase sun zama sanannun sakamako a gwajin SARS.
Ana ganin cutar alveolar da ta bazu, ƙwayoyin epithelial da kuma karuwar macrophages a cikin marasa lafiya da ke fama da SARS.
Kimanin kashi 20 zuwa 30 cikin 100 na marasa lafiya suna bukatar kulawa mai tsanani da kuma taimakon numfashi.
Baya ga ƙananan hanyoyin numfashi, gabobin jiki da dama, ciki har da gastrointestinal tube, hanta da koda, na iya kamuwa da cutar a cikin waɗannan mawuyacin hali, yawanci tare da hadari na cytokines, wanda zai iya zama mai kisa, musamman a cikin marasa lafiya masu rashin ƙarfi.
An fara gano cutar ne daga binciken da aka yi a cikin huhu na wani dangin wanda ya fara tafiya daga Guangzhou zuwa Hong Kong.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, an yi ƙoƙari sosai wajen bincike kan cutar coronavirus a cikin mutane.
HCoV-NL63 ya rabu da wani yaro mai wata bakwai daga Netherlands a ƙarshen 2004.
Da farko an gano cewa yana da yawa a cikin yara ƙanana, tsofaffi da marasa lafiya masu rashin lafiya da cututtukan numfashi.
Coriza, conjunctivitis, zazzabi da bronchiolitis sun zama ruwan dare a cikin cutar da HCoV-NL63 ta haifar.
Wani bincike na daban ya bayyana cewa an ware wannan kwayar daga samfurin hanci na wani yaro mai wata takwas da ke fama da cutar huhu a Netherlands.
Ko da yake an gano shi a Netherlands, a gaskiya an rarraba shi a duniya.
An kiyasta cewa HCoV-NL63 yana haifar da kusan kashi 4.7 cikin dari na cututtukan numfashi na yau da kullun, kuma mafi yawan cututtukan su suna faruwa a farkon bazara, bazara da hunturu.
HCoV-NL63 yana da alaƙa da cutar laryngitis ta obstructive, wanda aka fi sani da crup.
A shekarar nan, HCoV-HKU1 ya ware daga wani mutum mai shekaru 71 da aka kwantar da shi asibiti da ciwon huhu da bronchiolitis a Hong Kong.
Baya ga cutar huhu da kuma cutar sankarar hanta da aka samu a cikin al'umma, an bayar da rahoton cewa HCoV-HKU1 yana da alaƙa da matsanancin cutar asma.
Kamar HCoV-NL63, HCoV-229E, da HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 yana ko'ina cikin duniya kuma yana haifar da ƙananan cututtukan numfashi.
Wadannan mutane hudu da aka samu a cikin al'umma sun dace da mutane sosai kuma, gabaɗaya, ba su da wataƙila su canza don haifar da cututtukan cututtuka masu cutarwa, kodayake akwai haɗari daga dalilai da ba a sani ba, kamar a cikin wani abu da ba a saba gani ba na wani nau'in cutar HCoV-NL63, wanda kwanan nan aka ruwaito ya haifar da kamuwa da cutar ta hanyar numfashi a China.
Gabaɗaya, lokacin da waɗannan cututtukan coronavirus na ɗan adam suka sami ikon watsawa yadda ya kamata kuma su ci gaba da kasancewa a cikin ɗan adam, suma sun zama marasa ƙarfi ko masu cutarwa.
An fara ware cutar MERS-CoV a shekarar 2012 daga huhu na wani mutum mai shekaru 60 da haihuwa wanda ya kamu da cutar huhu mai tsanani da kuma rashin karfin koda a Saudiyya.
Ko da yake yawancin cututtuka da aka tabbatar a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje sun fito ne daga Gabas ta Tsakiya, an yi rahoton wasu cututtuka da aka shigo da su tare da kamuwa da cutar ta yau da kullum zuwa ga mutane da yawa a ƙasashen Turai da Tunisiya.
Wani yaduwar cutar ta biyu ta faru a Koriya ta Kudu a shekarar 2015 inda aka tabbatar da mutum 186.
Halin da ake nunawa a asibiti na MERS ya yi kama da na SARS, wanda ke nuna ci gaba da cutar huhu mai tsanani.
Ba kamar SARS ba, marasa lafiya da yawa da ke fama da cutar MERS sun kuma sami rashin lafiyar koda mai tsanani, wanda har zuwa yanzu MERS ne kawai ke faruwa a cikin cututtukan da cutar ta haifar da mutane.
Fiye da kashi 30 cikin dari na marasa lafiya suna da alamun gastrointestinal, kamar su diarrhea da kuma amai.
A ranar 14 ga Fabrairu, 2020, an tabbatar da fiye da 2500 a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje, tare da babban kisa na 34,4%, wanda ya sa MERS-CoV ya zama ɗayan ƙwayoyin cuta mafi lalacewa ga mutane da aka sani.
Daga tsakiyar zuwa ƙarshen Disamba na 2019, an gano tarin marasa lafiya da cutar huhu a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China, waɗanda a baya suka danganta da SARS-CoV-2.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta bayyana barkewar kamuwa da cutar ta hanyar numfashi ta kasa da ta haifar da SARS-CoV-2 a matsayin gaggawa na lafiyar jama'a na duniya kuma, a baya, ta kira cutar COVID-19.
A ranar 3 ga Maris, 2020, an tabbatar da shari'o'i 90 053 a duk duniya, tare da mutuwar 3,4%.
Abin lura, a birnin Hubei na kasar Sin, yawan mutuwa ya kai kashi 4.2 cikin dari, yayin da a wajen kasar, kashi 1.2 cikin dari.
SARS-CoV-2 yana haifar da kamuwa da cutar numfashi mai tsanani, kamar SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, wanda ke nunawa kamar zazzabi, tari da rashin numfashi.
An kuma lura da ciwon ciki a wasu marasa lafiya.
Ciwon huhu yana cikin alamun da suka fi tsanani kuma yana iya saurin zama ciwon numfashi mai tsanani.
Ko da yake SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV-2 sun yi kama da juna saboda babban homology na nucleotide na 82%, an rarraba su zuwa rassan daban-daban na itacen phylogenetic.
SARS-CoV-2 a bayyane yake ba shi da cutar, amma ya fi watsawa idan aka kwatanta da SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV.
An samu rahoton mutane marasa alamar cutar SARS-CoV-2, wanda zai iya taimakawa wajen yaduwar ta cikin sauri a duniya.
Idan aka kwatanta SARS-CoV-2 da sauran cututtukan coronavirus shida na mutum, ana gano kamanceceniya da bambance-bambance masu ban sha'awa.
Na farko, lokacin da ake yin kwayar cutar da tsawon lokacin da cutar ta coronavirus ke faruwa a cikin mutane suna kama da juna.
A wannan bangaren, SARS-CoV-2 ya bi al'amuran sauran cututtukan coronavirus shida na mutum.
Na biyu, tsanani na bayyanar cututtukan COVID-19 ya kasance tsakanin SARS-CoV da kuma kwayar cutar coronavirus guda hudu na mutane da aka samu a cikin al'umma (watau HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 da HCoV-NL63).
A gefe guda, kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 tana da halaye da aka fi gani a kamuwa da cutar coronavirus ta mutane da aka samu a cikin al'umma, wanda ya haɗa da gabatar da alamun bayyanar cututtuka marasa mahimmanci ko kuma marasa ƙarfi ko ma rashin bayyanar cututtuka.
A gefe guda kuma, an lura da ƙaramin ƙaramin ƙaramin ƙaramin COVID-19 kamar yadda yake faruwa da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV, kodayake alaƙar ta ɗan ragu.
Na uku, watsa SARS-CoV-2 kuma yana nuna wasu halaye masu ban sha'awa na coronavirus na mutane da aka samo a cikin al'umma da SARS-CoV.
A gefe guda, watsawar SARS-CoV-2 tana da sama da na kwayar cutar coronavirus da aka samu a cikin al'umma.
