ECDC da Ofishin Yankin Turai na WHO sun tsara jagororin da aka yi wa asibitoci da sabis na kiwon lafiya na farko don sake rarraba albarkatu a matakai daban-daban, wanda ya haɗa da mayar da hankali ga ayyukan dakin gwaje-gwaje kan gwajin COVID-19, soke hanyoyin zaɓin lokacin da zai yiwu, warewa da keɓe marasa lafiya masu COVID-19 da haɓaka ƙarfin kulawa mai tsanani ta hanyar horar da ma'aikata da haɓaka yawan masu numfashi da gado masu samuwa.
