A farkon da tsakiyar watan Janairu na shekarar 2020, cutar ta bazu zuwa wasu lardunan kasar Sin, wanda hakan ya haifar da ƙaurawar sabuwar shekara ta kasar Sin da kuma gaskiyar cewa Wuhan cibiyar sufuri ce da kuma babbar hanyar jirgin kasa.
A ranar 20 ga watan Janairu, kasar Sin ta ba da rahoton sabbin mutane 140 a rana guda, ciki har da mutane biyu a Beijing da kuma daya a Shenzhen.
Bayanai na hukuma na baya sun nuna cewa, a ranar 20 ga Janairu, 2020, mutane 6174 sun riga sun sami alamun cututtuka. A ranar 26 ga Maris, Amurka ta zarce China da Italiya tare da mafi yawan adadin waɗanda aka tabbatar da cutar a duniya. A ranar 9 ga Afrilu, 2020, an ba da rahoton fiye da miliyan 1.61 na cututtuka a duniya; sama da mutane 97,000 sun mutu kuma sama da 364,000 sun warke.
Kasashe da yankuna 200 sun yi akalla shari'ar guda ɗaya.
Saboda annobar a Turai, ƙasashe da yawa a cikin yankin Schengen sun ƙuntata 'yancin tafiya kuma sun kafa ƙuntatawa a kan iyakoki.
Sakamakon haka ya hada da matakan hanawa, kamar yin rigakafi (wanda ake kira umarnin zama a gida, umarnin samun mafaka a wurin ko kuma a tsare) da kuma dokar hana fita. A ranar 2 ga Afrilu, kimanin mutane miliyan 300, ko kusan kashi 90 cikin dari na yawan jama'a, suna bin wani nau'i na tsare a Amurka, fiye da mutane miliyan 50 suna tsare a Philippines, kimanin mutane miliyan 59 suna tsare a Afirka ta Kudu, kuma mutane miliyan 1300 suna tsare a Indiya.
A ranar 26 ga Maris, mutane miliyan 1700 a duniya suna cikin wani irin tsare-tsare, wanda ya karu zuwa mutane biliyan 2.6 bayan kwana biyu, wato kusan kashi ɗaya bisa uku na yawan duniya.
An fara samun mutum na farko da ya kamu da cutar COVID-19 a ranar 1 ga watan Disamba na shekarar 2019 a Wuhan; wani rahoto da ba a tabbatar da shi ba ya nuna cewa mutum na farko ya kamu da cutar a ranar 17 ga watan Nuwamba.
A ranar 26 ga watan Disamba, Dokta Zhang Jixian ta lura da wasu cututtukan cutar huhu da ba a san dalilin da ya sa ba, kuma asibitinta ta sanar da CDC na Jianghan na Wuhan a ranar 27 ga watan Disamba.
Gwajin kwayoyin halitta na farko na samfurin marasa lafiya a ranar 27 ga Disamba, 2019 ya nuna kasancewar coronavirus mai kama da SARS.
A ranar 31 ga watan Disamba, Hukumar Kula da Lafiya ta Wuhan ta fitar da wata sanarwa ta jama'a.
An sanar da Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya a ranar.
Yayin da ake yin wannan sanarwar, 'yan sanda sun gargadi likitoci a Wuhan saboda " yada jita-jita" game da barkewar cutar.
Hukumar Lafiya ta kasar Sin ta fara da cewa babu "hujja mai kyau" na yaduwar cutar tsakanin mutane.
A karshen watan Janairu, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta kaddamar da wani babban yunkuri, wanda sakataren jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin, Xi Jinping ya bayyana shi a matsayin "yaƙin jama'a", don dakile yaduwar cutar.
A cikin abin da aka bayyana a matsayin "babban kwanton a tarihin 'yan adam", a ranar 23 ga Janairu an sanar da dokar hana fita da fita daga Wuhan, wannan ya faɗaɗa zuwa birane 15 a Hubei, kuma ya shafi mutane miliyan 57.
An haramta amfani da motocin sirri a cikin birnin.
An soke bikin Sabuwar Shekarar Sin (25 ga Janairu) a wurare da yawa.
Hukumomi sun kuma sanar da gina asibiti na wucin gadi, asibitin Huoshenshan, wanda aka kammala cikin kwanaki 10.
Daga baya, an gina wani asibiti, asibitin Leishenshan, don karɓar ƙarin marasa lafiya.
Baya ga sabbin asibitocin da aka gina, kasar Sin ta kuma mayar da wasu wurare 14 a Wuhan, kamar cibiyoyin taro da filayen wasa, zuwa asibitocin wucin gadi. A ranar 26 ga Janairu, Gwamnati ta aiwatar da ƙarin matakan dakile barkewar COVID-19, wanda ya haɗa da bayar da sanarwar lafiya ga matafiya da kuma tsawaita hutun Bikin bazara.
An kuma rufe jami'o'i da makarantu a fadin kasar.
Yankunan Hong Kong da Macau sun aiwatar da wasu matakai, musamman ma a kan makarantu da jami'o'i.
An kafa matakan aiki na nesa a yankuna da dama na kasar Sin.
An sanya takunkumin tafiye-tafiye a ciki da wajen Hubei.
An sauya zirga-zirgar jama'a kuma an rufe gidajen tarihi na wucin gadi a duk faɗin ƙasar Sin.
An aiwatar da kula da motsi na jama'a a birane da dama, kuma an kiyasta cewa kusan mutane miliyan 760 (fiye da rabin yawan jama'a) sun fuskanci wasu nau'ikan ƙuntatawa a waje. Bayan fara fasalin barkewar cutar a duniya a watan Maris, hukumomin China sun ɗauki tsauraran matakai don hana " shigo da " cutar daga wasu ƙasashe.
Alal misali, Beijing ta sanya dokar killace-kwana ta kwanaki 14 ga duk matafiya na duniya da suka shiga birnin. A ranar 23 ga Maris, a cikin babban yankin China, an yi magana ne kawai a matakin ƙasa a cikin kwanaki biyar da suka gabata, a wannan lokacin, ta hanyar matafiyi wanda ya dawo daga Istanbul zuwa Canton.
A ranar 24 ga Maris, 2020, Firayim Ministan kasar Sin Li Keqiang ya ba da rahoton cewa an toshe yaduwar cututtukan da aka watsa a matakin ƙasa kuma an sarrafa barkewar cutar a China.
