Iran ta ba da riyal biliyan biyar don yaki da cutar.
A ranar 26 ga watan Fabrairun 2020, Shugaba Hassan Rouhani ya ce babu wani shiri na sanya wuraren da cutar ta shafa a cikin killace, kuma za a sanya mutane ne kawai a cikin killace.
A watan Maris, an sanar da tsare-tsaren rage tafiye-tafiye tsakanin birane, ko da yake zirga-zirga mai nauyi tsakanin birane sakamakon Sabuwar Shekarar Farisa Nowruz ya ci gaba.
Masallatai na Shi'a a Qom sun kasance a bude ga mahajjata har zuwa 16 ga Maris 2020. A watan Fabrairu, Iran ta zama cibiyar yada cutar bayan China.
