Angiotensin 2 (ECA2) mai canza enzyme enzyme ne wanda ke manne wa farfajiya ta waje (ƙwayoyin halitta) na ƙwayoyin huhu, jijiyoyi, zuciya, koda, da hanji.
ECA2 yana magance aikin enzymes masu canza angiotensin (ECA) ta hanyar rage adadin angiotensin II da haɓaka angiotensin (1-7), yana mai da shi manufa mai magani don maganin cututtukan zuciya. ECA2 kuma yana aiki a matsayin hanyar shiga sel don wasu coronavirus.
Ana kiran sigar mutum ta wannan enzyme hECA2.
Angiotensin 2 mai canza enzyme shine ƙarfe mai ƙunsar zinc kuma yana samuwa a saman ƙwayoyin endothelial da sauran nau'ikan.
Protein ECA2 yana dauke da wani yanki na N-terminal na peptidase M2 da kuma wani yanki na C-terminal na renal mai ɗaukar amino acid na colectrin.
ECA2 wani furotin ne mai laushi guda ɗaya na nau'i na I, tare da yankin enzymatically mai aiki a farfajiya a kan ƙwayoyin huhu da sauran kayan.
Ƙarfin ECA2 na waje na ƙwayoyin halitta yana rabu da ƙwayoyin halitta na transmembrane ta wani enzyme da ake kira shedase kuma a sakamakon haka, an saki furotin mai narkewa a cikin jini kuma a ƙarshe an fitar da shi ta cikin fitsari.
ECA2 yana cikin yawancin gabobin: ECA2 yana da alaƙa da ƙwayoyin halitta na ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin cuta na huhu na nau'i na II, ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin cuta na hanji, ƙwayoyin jini da ƙwayoyin endothelial na jini, da ƙwayoyin jijiyoyin jini na ƙwayoyin tsoka a yawancin gabobin.
Ana kuma samun maganganun ECA2 na mRNA a cikin ƙwaƙwalwar kwakwalwa, a cikin jiki, a cikin hypothalamus, da kuma a cikin ƙashin ƙwaƙwalwar ƙwaƙwalwa.
Babban aikin ECA2 shi ne ya magance ECA.
ECA ta cire hormone daga angiotensin I kuma ta samar da angiotensin II, wanda shi ne mai hana jini.
ECA2 kuma ya raba amino acid carboxyl-terminal phenylalanine daga angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) kuma ya hydrolyz shi don samar da angiotensin vasodilator (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ECA2 kuma yana iya raba wasu sauran peptides, ciki har da [des-Arg9]-bradiquinine, apoline, neurotensin, dinorphine A, da ghrelin.
ECA2 kuma yana daidaita zirga-zirgar membrane na SLC6A19 wanda ke dauke da amino acid mai tsaka tsaki kuma an danganta shi da cutar Hartnup.
A matsayin furotin na transmembrane, ECA2 yana aiki a matsayin babban wurin shiga ga wasu coronavirus, gami da HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virus da ke haifar da SARS); da SARS-CoV-2 (virus da ke haifar da COVID-19).
Musamman, haɗuwa da furotin S1 na SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV2 tare da ikon enzymatic na ECA2 a saman sel yana haifar da endocytosis da kuma canja wurin cutar tare da enzyme zuwa endosomes da ke cikin sel.
Wannan tsarin shigarwa kuma yana buƙatar shirya furotin S ta hanyar TMPRSS2 protease serine na mai masaukin, wanda a halin yanzu ana binciken hana shi a matsayin yiwuwar magani. Wannan ya haifar da wasu zato cewa rage matakan ECA2 a cikin kwayoyin zai iya taimakawa wajen yaki da kamuwa da cuta.
Duk da haka, kungiyoyi da kuma hukumomi da dama sun ba da shawarar ci gaba da maganin hana ECA da BRA.
Wani bita da aka yi da kuma nazarin da aka yi a kan tsarin da aka buga a ranar 11 ga Yuli, 2012 ya nuna cewa "ana amfani da maganin hana ECA don rage yawan cutar huhu da kashi 34 cikin dari idan aka kwatanta da shari'ar da aka yi da su".
Bugu da ƙari, "hadarin kamuwa da cutar huhu ya ragu a cikin marasa lafiya da aka yi musu magani da masu hana ECA kuma suna da haɗarin kamuwa da cutar huhu, musamman waɗanda ke fama da bugun jini da rashin zuciya.
Amfani da ECA inhibitors kuma ya shafi rage yawan mutuwa da ke tattare da cutar huhu, ko da yake sakamakon bai kasance mai ƙarfi ba ga haɗarin cutar huhu gaba ɗaya".
ECA2 na mutum (rhECA2) ya zama sabon magani don cutar huhu mai tsanani kuma ya inganta haemodynamics na huhu da kuma satar oxygen a cikin aladu da ke da cututtukan numfashi mai tsanani da lipopolysaccharides ke haifar.
Rayuwar rhECA2 a cikin mutane kusan awa 10 ne, kuma farkon aikinsa minti 30 ne, ban da tsawon sa'o'i 24.
Wasu binciken sun nuna cewa rhECA2 na iya zama magani mai ban sha'awa ga waɗanda ke fama da rashin haƙuri ga masu hana tsarin renin-angiotensin (sRA inhibitors) ko kuma a cikin cututtuka da ke da hawan jini na jini na II. An kimanta infusion na rhECA2 a cikin gwaji na asibiti don magance cutar ta fama da numfashi.
Aikace-aikacen COVID-19 aikace-aikacen software ne na na'urorin hannu waɗanda aka tsara don taimakawa tare da bin diddigin lambobin sadarwa don amsa cutar coronavirus ta 2019-2020, wato, tsarin gano mutanen ("lambobi") waɗanda zasu iya kasancewa cikin hulɗa da mutumin da aka kamu da cutar.
An ci gaba ko kuma an gabatar da aikace-aikace daban-daban tare da goyon bayan gwamnati a wasu yankuna da hukumomi.
An samar da tsarin da yawa don ƙirƙirar aikace-aikacen bin diddigin lamba.
Akwai damuwa game da sirrin sirri, musamman game da tsarin da ke dogara da bin diddigin yanayin masu amfani da aikace-aikacen.
Akwai wasu zaɓuɓɓuka masu sauƙi, kamar yin amfani da siginar Bluetooth don yin rikodin kusanci na mai amfani da wasu wayoyin hannu.
A ranar 10 ga Afrilu, 2020, Apple da Google sun sanar a hade cewa za su haɗa aikin don tallafawa waɗannan aikace-aikacen da ke kan Bluetooth kai tsaye a cikin tsarin aiki na iOS da Android.
A kasar Sin, gwamnatin kasar Sin, tare da Alipay, ta tura wani aikace-aikacen da ke ba 'yan kasar damar duba ko sun yi hulɗa da mutanen da ke da COVID-19.
Yanzu haka ana amfani da shi a birane 200 a kasar Sin. A Singapore ana amfani da wani app da ake kira TraceTogether.
An kirkiro aikace-aikacen ne ta hanyar ƙungiyar IT ta gida, an ƙaddamar da shi azaman aikace-aikacen buɗe tushen kuma za a ba da shi ga gwamnati. A Arewacin Macedonia an ƙaddamar da "StopKorona!", aikace-aikacen da ke dogara da Bluetooth don bin diddigin haɗarin waɗanda ke iya kamuwa da cutar da kuma ba da amsa mai sauri ga hukumomin lafiya.
Ma'aikatar Sadarwa da Fasaha da kuma Ma'aikatar Lafiya ne suka kirkiro wannan aikace-aikacen.
A ranar 14 ga Afrilu, 2020, aikace-aikacen yana jiran amincewa daga Google Play Store da Apple App Store.
A ranar 12 ga Afrilu, gwamnatin ta ba da rahoton cewa aikace-aikacen bin diddigin lamba yana cikin ci gaba da ci gaba kuma zai kasance a shirye don aiwatarwa a cikin makonni masu zuwa.
Kasashen Ostiraliya da New Zealand suna la'akari da aikace-aikacen da ke dogara da aikace-aikacen TraceTogether da kuma yarjejeniyar BlueTrace ta Singapore. Rasha na shirin gabatar da aikace-aikacen geoperimetry ga marasa lafiya da ke zaune a Moscow kuma sun sami binciken COVID-19, wanda aka tsara don tabbatar da cewa ba sa barin gidajensu.
Ross Anderson, farfesa a Jami'ar Cambridge na Kimiyyar Tsaro, ya fallasa matsaloli masu yawa na aiki tare da tsarin da ke dogara da aikace-aikace, gami da ƙididdigar ƙarya da yiwuwar rashin inganci idan karɓar aikace-aikacen ya iyakance ga ƙaramin ɓangare na yawan jama'a.
Dangane da damuwar game da yaduwar aikace-aikacen "coronavirus" masu yaudara ko cutarwa, Apple ya iyakance nau'ikan ƙungiyoyi waɗanda zasu iya ƙara aikace-aikacen da suka shafi coronavirus a cikin App Store zuwa ƙungiyoyin "masu hukuma" ko masu amincewa kawai.
Google da Amazon sun yi irin wannan takunkumin.
